# DASHBOARD DISPLAY GUIDELINES

## Personality Color Coding
- Neuroticism → Yellow  
- Agreeableness → Green  
- Conscientiousness → Blue  
- Openness → Purple  

## Metrics to Display
1. Response Rate (percentage of scam messages that receive replies)
2. Time to Scam Trigger (time taken before scammer asks for sensitive action)
3. Engagement Depth (number of messages exchanged before drop-off)

## Visual Success Indicators
- Green status: Scammer engaged for five or more messages
- Yellow status: Scammer requested WhatsApp or other external contact
- Red status: Scammer requested money, OTP, or sensitive information
